about.summary: pdb wrapper with remote access via tcp socket

name: rpdb
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rpdb" %}
{% set version = "0.1.6" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5d1a1cee34378ab075879dc30fa6328d448a9f680a66c4e84cac7382ad92f15f

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - rpdb

about:
  home: http://tamentis.com/projects/rpdb
  license: ISC (ISCL)
  license_family: OTHER
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.txt'
  summary: pdb wrapper with remote access via tcp socket
  dev_url: https://github.com/tamentis/rpdb

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Bezier89
    - pg-hbk
